SUMMARY:PhinneyWood Business Initiative Q&A
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the PNA to ask your questions about the BIA and what it means for the PhinneyWood business district This initiative represents a community-led effort to create a sustainable\, long-term framework for supporting and strengthening the neighborhood’s business district—built and guided by the people who live and invest here. \nRSVP HERE: PhinneyWood Business Initiative Meeting RSVP – Fill out form \nPlease note this meeting is intended for property owners and business owners. A meeting for the general public will be forthcoming at a later date. \nQuestions? Please reach out to the PNA’s Small Business Advocate\, Chris Maykut at chrism@phinneycenter.org
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/phinneywood-business-initiative-qa/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus: Blue (upper) Building\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
CATEGORIES:PhinneyWood
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://media.phinneycenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/18073325/PhinneyWood_2.jpg
END:VEVENT
