SUMMARY:Boutique Bellydancersize Classes
DESCRIPTION:Explore the ancient & mysterious art of belly dancing\, with Boutique Bellydancersize classes! \nSpecialized classes. Superior core workout. Strengthens & coordinates muscle groups in the trunk\, spine & arms. Improves posture & flexibility. Students will learn the basic steps\, undulations\, shimmies\, isolations\, tuxseem and more. \nAll Ages. \nGroup classes at Phinney Center. A focused gym that provides a sense of connection. Zaphara’s classes go beyond physical fitness\, including a broader sense of self care\, including sleep\, nutrition\, skin health\, stress management & socializing. \nStarts the 1st Thursday of the Month \n7:00 pm – 8:00 pm – Beginners \n7:45 pm – 9:00 pm Intermediate – Advanced \n4 weeks: $80\, Drop-ins: $27 per class \nTaught by Zaphara\, Master Bellydance Instructor & Performer \nSign up and pay online: bellydancingbyzaphara.com/classes
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/boutique-bellydancersize-classes/2026-04-09/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus: Blue (upper) Building\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
CATEGORIES:Renter Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://media.phinneycenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/30135720/zaphara.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Belly Dancing by Zaphara":MAILTO:bellydancingbyzaphara@comcast.net
END:VEVENT
